conexp.fx.core.algorithm.exploration

Class AttributeExploration<G,M>

  • java.lang.Object
    • conexp.fx.core.algorithm.exploration.AttributeExploration<G,M>
  • Type Parameters:
    G - the type of objects.
    M - the type of attributes.

    public final class AttributeExploration<G,M>
extends Object
    The standard attribute exploration algorithm. This implementation is wrapped around the NextImplication class, that computes the formal implications in the canonical base of a formal context by means of the NextClosure algorithm.
